				<p>I don't receive too much email spam these days. Thank you gmail. But it seems like I'll soon need some sort of filter for my physical mail box as well. Especially annoying: I gave the WWF some money only to now constantly have them harass me for more. <a href="http://paul-m-jones.com/?p=36">Rule 2</a> at work.</p>
<p><img src="http://static.thinkingphp.org/img/mail-spam.jpg"></p>
